\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Proof
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $y\in\text{coni}\left(C\right)$
\end_inset

.
 Then 
\begin_inset Formula $y=\sum_{i=1}^{m}\alpha_{i}x_{i}$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha_{i}\geq0$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}\in C$
\end_inset

.
 If 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha_{i}=0$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 then 
\begin_inset Formula $y=0$
\end_inset

 immediately in 
\begin_inset Formula $\bigcup_{x\in C}\left\{ \gamma x\big|x\in C,\,\gamma\geq0\right\} $
\end_inset

.
