\end_inset

 is bounded but there exists some 
\begin_inset Formula $z\in\mathcal{R}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in C$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $x+\lambda z\in C$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\geq0$
\end_inset

.
